//|					  Correct the datatype of the generated   |
//|					  ALPA dummy to 11 from 1.		  |
//|   0.2    14-Sep-2010    Carolyn Y     Dummy fill rule update to 20100908 :	  |
//|					  Add DUMBM layer to block all metal      |
//|					  dummies filled.			  |
